# Frontend guardrails (CheetahFlow)

- **API:** add new backend calls in `frontend/src/lib/api.ts` only — keep fetch logic centralized (browser uses same-origin `/api/v1/...` via Next rewrites).
- **Types:** extend `frontend/src/types/index.ts` to match backend Pydantic schemas; avoid duplicating ad-hoc interfaces in random files.
- **Styling:** Tailwind utility classes; avoid inline styles except for unavoidable third-party widgets.
- **Layout:** pages under `src/app/dashboard/`; reusable UI under `src/components/ui/`; feature code under `src/components/<feature>/`.
